<collectingCountry box="[806,873,1053,1079]" name="Spain" pageId="53" pageNumber="54">Spain</collectingCountry>
; also North Africa. 
<collectingCountry box="[1096,1195,1053,1079]" name="Portugal" pageId="53" pageNumber="54">Portugal</collectingCountry>
: two provinces in the north and two provinces in the far south.
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="53.[151,1436,1016,1259]" pageId="53" pageNumber="54">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,300,1125,1151]" pageId="53" pageNumber="54">Ecology.</emphasis>
Recorded in 
<collectingCountry box="[448,543,1125,1151]" name="Portugal" pageId="53" pageNumber="54">Portugal</collectingCountry>
from Mediterranean forest, brackish marshes and a river bank. Thus far its ecology was entirely unknown.
</paragraph>
